Package: bananarama
Title: Generate Presentation Images Using Google Gemini
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Generate presentation images using Google Gemini's image generation
    capabilities (nanobanana). Define images in a YAML configuration file with
    support for reference images, style defaults, and image dependencies.
